data.description:
Welcome to paradise! This exquisite 2 bedroom, 2 bathroom home is a true waterfront retreat. Nestled on a deep water direct access canal, you'll have unparalleled access to the water and endless opportunities for boating and water activities.

Step inside and be captivated by the recently updated galley kitchen, complete with top-of-the-line appliances, sleek countertops, and plenty of cabinet space. The tile flooring throughout adds a touch of sophistication, while the Florida room, equipped with power shades, offers a tranquil space to unwind and admire the picturesque surroundings.

One of the highlights of this property is the solar heated pool, providing the perfect setting for relaxation and entertainment all year round. Imagine taking a refreshing dip in the crystal-clear water while basking in the warm Florida sun. The beautiful landscaping and grassy rear yard create a serene atmosphere, perfect for outdoor gatherings or simply enjoying the lush surroundings.

Boating enthusiasts will appreciate the newer dock, a gateway to exploring the stunning waterways at your leisure. Whether you're an avid boater or simply enjoy watching the boats go by, this feature is sure to impress. Additionally, the home offers a convenient laundry room and a single-car garage for your storage and parking needs.

Don't miss the chance to experience the ultimate waterfront lifestyle in this meticulously maintained home. Schedule a showing today and let this dream property become your own personal haven.
